GET TO KNOW US
KULIT KULIT CHEESE CRISPY . Popiah skin, traditionally used in Asian cuisine to make fresh spring rolls, takes on a new and exciting role in the creation of KK Cheese. This thin and crispy wrapper serves as the base for a sensation that will have your taste buds dancing with delight. It's a perfect harmony of textures and flavors, creating a truly unforgettable snack.
Whether you're hosting a party, enjoying a movie night, or simply craving a tasty treat, KK Cheese is the perfect choice. Its unique combination makes it a standout snack that is sure to impress your family and friends.
 
MOST RECOMMENDED: (FOR FIRST TIME CUSTOMER)
BUNDLE OF 4 MIXED - 2 CHEESE , 1 SALTED EGG, 1 TOMATO
***IF YOU WILL LIKE TO CUSTOMIZE YOUR OWN FLAVOURS(or add seaweed wasabi), KINDLY ORDER BUNDLE OF 4 MIX AND INDICATE UNDER MESSAGE/COMMENT TO SELLER YOUR PREFERRED FLAVOURS!!***



FLAVOURS: 
 
CHEESE (THE OG)
This is the ultimate BOMB!!! BEING THE OG OF THE SNACK, THIS WILL FUFIL YOUR SNACK DESIRES. SUPER SAVOURY, CHEESY, CRISPY, ADDICTIVE AND PACKS WITH A PUNCH OF SPICE. NOTHING LIKE YOU HAVE EATEN OUTSIDE. 
Best for pairing this to go with your favourite movies/shows or share at gatherings. One of our favourite among the 3 flavours. Highly recommended. You will not regret!!
ING LIST: POPIAH SKI, VEGETABLE OIL, PREMIUM CHEESE, CHILLI & SUGAR. NO ALLIUMS
 
SALTED EGG (FOR THE PEOPLE WHO LOVE SALTED EGG)
Salted egg GAO!!! Generously coated with salted egg. and stirred with butter and chilli to entice your tastebuds. 
ING LIST: POPIAH SKI, SALT, BUTTER, VEGETABLE OIL, PREMIUM SALTED EGG, CURRY LEAVES, CHILLI & SUGAR. NO ALLIUMS BUT HAVE EGG.
 
TOMATO 
A Sweet and Sour combination which leaves your tongue asking for more. Favourite among kids too!! The spice level is low making it suitable for consumption for those who do not take much spice. Our kids (3,6 years old) love this! alot of our customers who do not take tomato snacks turned into a convert after eating this.
ING LIST: POPIAH SKI, VEGETABLE OIL, SALT, TOMATO POWDER, CHILLI, GLUCOSE, SUGAR. NO ALLIUMS
 
SEAWEED WASABI (NEW!!!) 
That nori seaweed feels, with hint of wasabi hotness coming and creeping up your tongue. Burst of flavours! Newly launch on 25/3/2024. LIMITED STOCKS.





***IF YOU WILL LIKE TO CUSTOMIZE YOUR OWN FLAVOURS, KINDLY ORDER BUNDLE OF 4 MIX AND INDICATE UNDER MESSAGE/COMMENT TO SELLER YOUR PREFERRED FLAVOURS!!***
 
IS THIS HALAL?
We have honestly came across this question many times thus we will like to clear the air here. Our product is currently going under halal certification and thus the certificate is not out yet. Our product ingredients are ALL halal certified and facility is only producing KK CHEESE to avoid contamination.
Why is the certification not out yet??
1) Halal certification is a tedious process especially for new brands.
2) Supplier has even changed our factory space as the old one is not according to their layout standard. 
3) All the changes requires time, and we aim to have the product halal certified by this year.

💡Easy installation:
(1) First, test whether the light can light up normally
(2) Wipe the area that needs to be installed clean with a clean cloth and dry thoroughly
(3) Tear off the tape and press the light strip tightly where it needs to be installed. Do not tear it off after installation, otherwise it may easily cause the light strip to tear open
(4) Power on the USB and plug it into the power supply. It is important to note that the controller should not be suspended in the air, otherwise it may cause loose connections

📌Attention: When the USB power is turned on, the light strip does not light up
(1) Please check and replace the USB plug at the customer's home or try plugging it into a different socket
(2) Align the black controller V+with the arrow, otherwise it may cause a short circuit. If it doesn't light up, please unplug the rotating front and back sides and reconnect
📌After connecting the USB power supply, the light strip experiences abnormal low frequency and dim light
(1)Please try replacing with another USB socket, as this is caused by insufficient power. The power of the power bank will be lower than the normal socket power, and different USB sockets have different power, which can lead to this situation.
📌Remote control not working properly
(1) To remove the card from the back of the remote control, press ON to continue operating other function buttons
(2) The direction of the remote control should be aligned with the direction of the black receiving line
📌Can the remote control replace the battery
(1) The remote control contains a C2025-2032 button battery, which can be replaced according to the operating instructions on the remote control
📌Bluetooth cannot be connected
(1) Ensure that the Bluetooth of the phone is turned on
(2) Ensure that the APP has been authorized to enable Bluetooth functionality
[Settings] - [Lotus Lantern] - [bluetooth]
(3) If it still doesn't work, please uninstall the app and reinstall it

A2:You can add water, not too much. A small amount several times. Test the feeling while adding water. Don't add a lot of water at once, it will make slime irreparable
 
Q3:How to save slime？
A3: It is recommended that children return it to the box and store it after not playing. Ensure that there is no long-term contact with the air.

Sturdy and durable: Made of ABS shell and steel wire rope, ensuring long-lasting use.
 
Convenient buckle: The extra large outdoor buckle can be easily fastened on bags or pants with a simple press.
 
Retractable wire rope: With a built-in spring, the wire rope can be freely stretched up to 60cm for versatile use.
 
Portable and lightweight: Small in size and easy to carry, making it perfect for outdoor activities like hiking and camping.
 
Versatile usage: Suitable for various occasions, including mountain climbing, hiking, and camping.
 
 
                        Description:
 
                        Introducing our retractable carabiner Keychain, the perfect accessory to keep your keys and cards secure and easily accessible. Made with a 1mm diameter stainless steel wire rope, this keychain is not only durable but also smooth PVC-coated for added protection. With a maximum stretch length of 65cm, it can carry up to 50kg, making it ideal for your daily needs.
 
The retractable key ring features a corrosion-resistant metal ring, tear-resistant parachute cord, and an ABS material badge holder. Its built-in flexible spring and wire rope allow you to access your keys and cards without removing the key ring from your bag or belt. The ABS shell and steel wire rope construction ensure sturdiness and durability.
 
With its extra-large outdoor buckle opening, this keychain can be easily fastened on bags or pants by simply pressing inward. The buckle is designed to be simple and convenient to use. Additionally, the wire rope rebound device has a built-in spring that allows the wire rope to be freely retracted and stretched up to approximately 60cm.
 
Compact and lightweight, this keychain is easy to carry and store, making it suitable for various occasions such as outdoor mountain climbing, hiking, camping, and more.

Instructions for use:
-Wash before using
-Owala brand products are designed to be as simple and easy to clean as possible. Best practices for cleaning each part may vary
-Lids: All lids are top-rack dishwasher safe and designed for easy cleaning. The spout gasket should be removed by using the convenient pull tab and cleaned separately. A sponge or straw brush can be used to access the nook or smaller spaces. Soaking the parts in distilled white vinegar beforehand will help breakup buildup in inaccessible areas
-Straws: The straws can be easily removed and put in the dishwasher’s silverware bin
-Cup: Hand-wash with warm, soapy water
-Avoid accidental opening of the bottle by keeping the button free and clear of other objects. Cover the button with the loop to help avoid accidental pushing of the button
 
Warnings:
-Do not microwave, freeze, or boil
-In order to minimize bacterial growth, do not use to store warm dairy products, baby food, or other perishable liquids
-Not for use with hot, carbonated, or perishable liquids
-Altitude changes (such as during airplane travel or while ascending mountains), or exposure to hot temperatures (such as leaving the bottle in a car on a hot day) may cause pressure to build up in the bottle and may cause the contents to leak or spray when opening the bottle. To prevent this, loosen the lid by a quarter turn to release pressure; then retighten the lid
before drinking
-Pressurized contents may cause the spout cover to open rapidly enough to injure fingers positioned in or near the recess behind the spout cover
-When opening the bottle, keep fingers away from the recess behind the spout cover
-Always open with caution

Introducing the Coffeehock Limited Edition Glass Cup – your perfect companion for coffee moments, designed with meticulous attention to detail and practicality.
First and foremost, let's talk about its innovative leak-proof silicon seal. No more worries about spills or leaks when you're on the go. This cup keeps your coffee safe and secure, whether it's in your bag or on your desk.

Cleaning up after your coffee session is a breeze with this cup. Its simple design makes it easy to disassemble and clean, so you can spend less time washing dishes and more time enjoying your coffee.
However, it's important to remember that as a glass cup, sudden changes in temperature can cause it to crack. So, handle it with care and avoid extreme temperature changes to keep your cup looking pristine for years to come.
In summary, the Coffeehock Limited Edition Glass Cup is not just a cup – it's a carefully crafted companion for your coffee adventures, featuring a leak-proof seal, a stylish leather sleeve for heat protection, a glass straw for added convenience, and easy cleaning.
